snippet.title: I'm looking for 3024 people | Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
The dead computer engineer had only one purpose, to reveal the true face of the company he worked for. Now, this mission is up to a hacker and 3024 people.

"I'm looking for 3024 people" is an alternate reality game produced by Bakodun Game Studios. In this adventure; you will have to infiltrate the company using a hacking program developed by Frank and anonym52, examine the leaked documents, and perform your own tasks.

Watch Frank's Message: https://youtu.be/MmSn5JM6E80

You can find all the details about the mission on this website: https://www.frankscomputer.online/
The Mission: https://www.frankscomputer.online/the-mission
Special Area: https://www.frankscomputer.online/special-area
Discord: https://discord.com/invite/uUV6yQhzSK
NFTs: https://opensea.io/collection/im-looking-for-3024-people

Bakodun Game Studios: https://www.bakodungamestudios.com
